(640, '<1436114098.14.561.990.609691039@qq.com>', '好消息：你有1次参与竞猜领豪礼的机会(AD)', '<html>\r\n	<head>\r\n		<title></title>\r\n	</head>\r\n	<body><img src="http://dm.ed10.org/obWFpbD02MDk2OTEwMzlAcXEuY29tJmlkPTE0LjU2MS45OTAmdGltZT0yMDE1MDcwNjAwJm1vZHVsYXI9MTIwMSZnb3RvPTEzNjE0OTU=" border=0 width=0>\r\n		<table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="668">\r\n			<tbody>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td>\r\n						<a href="http://dm.ed10.org/cbWFpbD02MDk2OTEwMzlAcXEuY29tJmlkPTE0LjU2MS45OTAmdGltZT0yMDE1MDcwNjAwJm1vZHVsYXI9MTIwMSZnb3RvPTEzNjE0OTY=" target="_blank"><img border="0" height="454" src="http://image.ed10.org/imags/yinghua/yinghuagai_01.jpg" width="301" /></a></td>\r\n					<td>\r\n						<a href="http://dm.ed10.org/cbWFpbD02MDk2OTEwMzlAcXEuY29tJmlkPTE0LjU2MS45OTAmdGltZT0yMDE1MDcwNjAwJm1vZHVsYXI9MTIwMSZnb3RvPTEzNjE0OTc=" target="_blank"><img border="0" height="454" src="http://image.ed10.org/imags/yinghua/yinghuagai_02.jpg" width="367" /></a></td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td colspan="2">\r\n						<a href="http://dm.ed10.org/cbWFpbD02MDk2OTEwMzlAcXEuY29tJmlkPTE0LjU2MS45OTAmdGltZT0yMDE1MDcwNjAwJm1vZHVsYXI9MTIwMSZnb3RvPTEzNjE0OTg=" target="_blank"><img border="0" height="222" src="http://image.ed10.org/imags/yinghua/yinghuagai_03.jpg" width="668" /></a></td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td colspan="2">\r\n						<a href="http://dm.ed10.org/cbWFpbD02MDk2OTEwMzlAcXEuY29tJmlkPTE0LjU2MS45OTAmdGltZT0yMDE1MDcwNjAwJm1vZHVsYXI9MTIwMSZnb3RvPTEzNjE0OTk=" target="_blank"><img border="0" height="250" src="http://image.ed10.org/imags/yinghua/yinghuagai_04.jpg" width="668" /></a></td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td colspan="2" style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; padding:0px 7px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n						日本为什么称为“樱花之国 ”? 日本的樱花有几百个品种，一般分为染井吉野（淡红白色）、山樱（淡红白色）、大岛樱（白色）、江户彼岸樱（白色或红紫色）、枝垂樱（红色）等。受气温的影响，樱花由温暖的日本列岛南端向北方沿着纬度依次开放，因此形成一条由南向北推进的“樱前线”。日本有句俗语叫“樱花七日”，就是说一朵樱花从开放到凋谢大约为七天，整棵樱树从开花到全谢大约半月左右。</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td align="right" colspan="2" style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px; padding:5px 7px;">\r\n						<font color="#666666">如看不到内容，请点击<a href="http://dm.ed10.org/cbWFpbD02MDk2OTEwMzlAcXEuY29tJmlkPTE0LjU2MS45OTAmdGltZT0yMDE1MDcwNjAwJm1vZHVsYXI9MTIwMSZnb3RvPTEzNjE1MDA=" style=" color:#EC75B0; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank">浏览</a></font>；如不需要，可以点击<a href="http://dm.ed10.org/cbWFpbD02MDk2OTEwMzlAcXEuY29tJmlkPTE0LjU2MS45OTAmdGltZT0yMDE1MDcwNjAwJm1vZHVsYXI9MTIwMSZnb3RvPTEzNjE1MDE=" style=" color:#EC75B0; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank">退订</a></td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n			</tbody>\r\n		</table>\r\n	</body>\r\n</html>', '', '樱花国际日语|cartoon@culture.sakura.com', '609691039@qq.com', 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 1436114108, '2015-07-09 14:13:03'),
